body:
Sorry for taking so long to respond, I haven't had access to my project for a bit so I had no way of testing.

Anyway, upgrading to 0.3.1 (`git checkout 0.3.1`) and running `./compile.sh` leaves me with: 
`gRPC Java plugin not found in`
followed by nothing (I know there's supposed to be an error message here usually).

As said, I haven't touched the system since the last post so Java should still be where I left it. I'll try to fix this and see if upgrading to 0.3.1 helped.
